  "full_text": "An update for gcc-toolset-15-gcc is now available for Red Hat Enterprise Linux 10.\n\nThe gcc-toolset-15-gcc package contains the GNU Compiler Collection version 15.Bug Fix(es) and Enhancement(s): GTS15-gcc: Toolchain rebase [rhel-8.10.z] (JIRA:RHEL-92246)  gcc-toolset-15-offload-nvptx is missing [RHEL-8] (JIRA:RHEL-95056)  gcc-toolset-15-gcc-plugin-annobin is missing [RHEL-8] (JIRA:RHEL-95057)  Build gcc-toolset-15-gcc with with pie and bind-now [el8] (JIRA:RHEL-95594)  [GTS15] link fails when using -Wl,--as-needed [rhel-8.10.z] (JIRA:RHEL-94867)  GTS GCC doesn't ship libstdc++.modules.json [rhel-8] (JIRA:RHEL-97091)"
